---
layout: base.njk
title: "Rashid Al-Ma'awali | Mechatronics Engineering Portfolio"
description: "Portfolio of Rashid Al-Ma'awali, a Mechatronics Engineering student focused on embedded control, electropneumatics, robotics, and soft robotic systems."
ogDescription: "Embedded control, electropneumatics, robotics, CAD design, and research-oriented soft robotics systems."
heroCanvas: true
---
<main id="main">
  <section class="hero section-pad">
    <div class="container hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Mechatronics Engineering Student · Muscat, Oman</p>
        <p class="status-pill"><span class="status-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>Currently: Research Assistant — soft robotic rehabilitation, SQU</p>
        <h1>Embedded control, electropneumatics, and robotics that <em class="grad-text">survive the bench</em>.</h1>
        <p class="hero-lede">
          I am a Mechatronics Engineering student at Sultan Qaboos University focused on practical hardware-software systems: soft robotics, sensor feedback, pneumatic actuation, control logic, CAD design, and technical documentation.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button button-primary" href="/projects/">View projects</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/resume/">Résumé</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="{{ site.github }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="{{ site.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
        <div class="signal-row" aria-label="Core areas">
          <span>Embedded Control</span>
          <span>Electropneumatics</span>
          <span>Robotics</span>
          <span>Mechanical CAD</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="hero-panel" aria-label="Illustrative bench readout from the rehabilitation-glove controller">
        <div class="panel-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <figure class="scope" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="scope-head">
            <span class="scope-title">bench · scope</span>
            <span class="scope-status"><span class="status-dot"></span>live</span>
          </div>
          <div class="scope-screen">
            <svg class="scope-svg" viewBox="0 0 320 160" preserveAspectRatio="none" focusable="false">
              <path class="trace trace-1" d="M0,120 C40,120 62,44 100,44 S164,44 200,64 C240,86 284,44 320,44"></path>
              <path class="trace trace-2" d="M0,140 L60,140 L60,92 L140,92 L140,132 L220,132 L220,72 L300,72 L320,72"></path>
            </svg>
            <canvas class="scope-canvas" data-canvas="scope" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
          </div>
          <figcaption class="scope-legend">
            <span class="ch ch1">CH1 flex</span>
            <span class="ch ch2">CH2 pressure</span>
            <span class="ch ch3">PID · FSM</span>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <div class="metrics-grid">
          <div><strong data-count="2027">2027</strong><span>Expected graduation</span></div>
          <div><strong data-count="3.29" data-decimals="2">3.29</strong><span>GPA / 4.00</span></div>
          <div><strong data-scramble>C2</strong><span>English (CEFR)</span></div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad border-top" id="about">
    <div class="container split-section">
      <div class="section-heading" data-reveal="left">
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h2>Engineering is where ideas meet wiring, tolerances, and inconvenient reality.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content-stack" data-reveal>
        <p>My work sits at the intersection of mechanical design, embedded firmware, controls, and pneumatic actuation. I enjoy building systems that move, sense, respond, and provide measurable feedback rather than remaining as clean diagrams on paper.</p>
        <p>I value clear documentation, practical testing, and honest limitations. A design that works only in a slide deck is decoration; a design that survives troubleshooting earns respect.</p>
        <div class="signal-row" aria-label="Research interests">
          <span>Soft robotic actuation</span>
          <span>Tele-rehabilitation</span>
          <span>Embedded control</span>
          <span>Sensor feedback &amp; instrumentation</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad border-top" id="projects">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading wide" data-reveal>
        <p class="eyebrow">Selected Engineering Projects</p>
        <h2>A few representative builds — hardware, firmware, CAD, testing, and documentation.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="project-grid">
        {%- for p in collections.projects %}
        {%- if p.data.highlight %}
        <article class="project-card{{ ' featured' if p.data.featured }}" data-domain="{{ p.data.domain }}" data-reveal style="--si: {{ loop.index0 % 2 }}">
          <div class="project-visual" style="view-transition-name: proj-{{ p.fileSlug }}">
            {%- if p.data.thumbnail %}
            {% image p.data.thumbnail, (p.data.cardTitle or p.data.caseTitle or p.data.title), "(min-width: 760px) 540px, 100vw" %}
            {%- else %}
            <span class="chip-icon" aria-hidden="true">{{ p.data.chip or "ESP32" }}</span>
            {%- endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="project-kicker">{{ p.data.kicker }}</p>
            <h3>{{ p.data.cardTitle or p.data.caseTitle or p.data.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ p.data.summary }}</p>
            {%- set ctags = p.data.cardTags or p.data.tags %}
            {%- if ctags %}<div class="tag-row">{% for t in ctags %}{% if loop.index <= 5 %}<span>{{ t }}</span>{% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}
            {%- if (p.data.hasCaseStudy and p.url) or p.data.repo %}
            <div class="card-actions">
              {%- if p.data.hasCaseStudy and p.url %}<a class="card-link" href="{{ p.url }}">Read case study →</a>{% endif %}
              {%- if p.data.repo %}<a href="{{ p.data.repo }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Repository</a>{% endif %}
            </div>
            {%- endif %}
          </div>
        </article>
        {%- endif %}
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>

      <div class="hero-actions" data-reveal>
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/projects/">View all projects →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad border-top" id="research">
    <div class="container split-section">
      <div class="section-heading" data-reveal="left">
        <p class="eyebrow">Research &amp; Leadership</p>
        <h2>Research and student leadership with real technical responsibility.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline">
        <article class="timeline-item" data-reveal>
          <span class="timeline-date">Jun 2026</span>
          <h3>Research Assistant · Soft Robotic Actuators &amp; Tele-Rehabilitation</h3>
          <p class="muted">Sultan Qaboos University, College of Engineering</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Building and validating the control system for a soft robotic rehabilitation glove.</li>
            <li>Developing ROS 2/micro-ROS integration for motion-pattern adjustment and real-time logging.</li>
            <li>Preparing technical documentation covering architecture, testing, and engineering recommendations.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="timeline-item" data-reveal>
          <span class="timeline-date">Jul 2024 – Jul 2025</span>
          <h3>President, Projects Committee · Free Open-Source Software Society</h3>
          <p>Led project-committee planning, supported technical workshop organization, and coordinated with society members, faculty, and student teams.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="timeline-item" data-reveal>
          <span class="timeline-date">Jul 2023 – Jul 2024</span>
          <h3>Vice President, Projects Committee · Mechatronics Engineering Society</h3>
          <p>Coordinated technical logistics, venue arrangements, and team registration for a university-wide robotics event.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad border-top" id="skills">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading wide" data-reveal>
        <p class="eyebrow">Technical Stack</p>
        <h2>Skills grouped by how they are used in real systems.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <article class="skill-card" data-reveal style="--si: 0"><h3>Embedded &amp; Control</h3><p>C/C++, Python, MATLAB, ESP32, Arduino, AVR, ROS 2, micro-ROS, serial telemetry, sensor interfacing, finite-state machines, control systems.</p></article>
        <article class="skill-card" data-reveal style="--si: 1"><h3>Mechanical &amp; Pneumatic</h3><p>SOLIDWORKS, AutoCAD, Fusion 360, machine design, pneumatics/hydraulics, electropneumatics, pumps, valves, mechanical CAD.</p></article>
        <article class="skill-card" data-reveal style="--si: 2"><h3>Documentation &amp; Leadership</h3><p>Technical reports, GitHub documentation, project coordination, team leadership, workshop organization, communication.</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad border-top" id="resume">
    <div class="container resume-grid">
      <div class="section-heading" data-reveal="left">
        <p class="eyebrow">Resume Snapshot</p>
        <h2>Mechatronics Engineering at Sultan Qaboos University.</h2>
        <p class="muted">Expected graduation: June 2027 · Muscat, Oman</p>
        <p><a class="button button-secondary" href="/resume/">View full résumé →</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-card" data-reveal>
        <h3>Education</h3>
        <p><strong>Sultan Qaboos University</strong> — B.Sc. in Mechatronics Engineering</p>
        <p>Coursework includes Control Systems, Embedded Systems, Instrumentation &amp; Measurements, Pneumatics &amp; Hydraulics, Electromechanical Systems &amp; Actuators, Machine Design, Mechatronics System Design, Thermal Sciences, and Modelling &amp; Simulation.</p>
        <h3>Certifications</h3>
        <p>Basics of AutoCAD · NVIDIA Fundamentals of Deep Learning · SQU Certificate of Excellence · Fundamentals of Python</p>
        <h3>Languages</h3>
        <p>Arabic: Native · English: CEFR C2 Proficiency via goFLUENT</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad contact-section" id="contact">
    <div class="container contact-card" data-reveal="scale">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
      <h2>Interested in embedded systems, robotics, controls, or research collaboration?</h2>
      <p>I'm open to graduate research opportunities and collaborations in robotics, control, and soft-robotic systems. Reach me by email, LinkedIn, or GitHub — phone is kept off the public site to spare it from spam bots.</p>
      <div class="contact-actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">Email me</a>
        <button class="button button-secondary copy-email" type="button" data-email="{{ site.email }}" data-label="Copy email" aria-live="polite">Copy email</button>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="{{ site.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="{{ site.github }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
